<page>
    <shortlink>ux controlbar items disclosure settings display type property</shortlink>
    <topic>Display type</topic>
    <description>Specify where the disclosure should be shown.</description>
    <discussion>
        <p>The *[ui:Display type]* defines where a disclosure is shown. The available options are:</p>
    </discussion>
    <sections>
        <section>
            <list bullet="true">
                <item>
                    <name>expand-before</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>expand-after</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>expand-element</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>expand-element-cover</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>extend</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>extend-element</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>extend-element-cover</name>
                </item>
                <item build="4740">
                    <name>flyout</name>
                </item>
                <item build="4740">
                    <name>flyout-element</name>
                </item>
                <item build="4740">
                    <name>flyout-element-cover</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>cover</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>outside-before</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>outside-after</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>screen-left</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>screen-right</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>screen-top</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>screen-bottom</name>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>explicit</name>
                </item>
            </list>
        </section>
        <section build="">
            <title>Disclosures as Menus</title>
            <description>
                <p>The flyout types allow you to create disclosures that look like menus. For example, the *[ui:flyout-element]* positions the disclosure relative to the button or link that was clicked to display the disclosure:</p>
            </description>
            <figure>
                <link>images/flyoutelementcontrolbar.jpg</link>
            </figure>
        </section>
        <section>
            <description>
                <p>There are several ControlBar templates available that demonstrate disclosures as menus using the *[ui:flyout-element]* type. ControlBar templates can be created using the [Load Sample ControlBar] link on the ControlBar Builder Home tab.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
    </sections>
    <links>
